These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, water
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, superhero, epic
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, sudoku, woodworking
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, prince, bluemaster
1. the person watching superhero movies is the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is in the middle##1
6. the person drinking water is the person watching epic movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Beverage      | water  | juice       | mirinda   |
| Movie-Genre          | epic | scientific | superhero |
| Hobby         | chess  | woodworking | sudoku    |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | davidoff       | prince      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, potato, radish
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, chef
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, italian, turkish
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, almond-milk
1. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating radish is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the bartender is on the right of the italian##1
4. the chef is on the left of the doctor##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Food          | pear      | potato  | radish        |
| Job         | chef | doctor | bartender |
| Nationality   | brazilian | italian | turkish       |
| Beverage           | almond-milk     | tea     | 7up      |

