.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, fuchsia, pink
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, dancer, software-developer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, zombie
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, indonesian, australian
1. the software-developer is the turkish##1
2. the indonesian is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
3. the dancer is on the left of the turkish##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the software-developer##1
6. the person who likes pink is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Color      | fuchsia    | purple        | pink |
| Job           | dancer    | software-developer | chef    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | zombie             | satire  |
| Nationality     | australian     | turkish                | indonesian  |

