.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, pall-mall, cain
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, fisherman, lawyer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, horror, western
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, spanish, mexican
1. the mexican is on the right of the spanish##1
2. the cain-smoker is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the turkish is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is the mexican##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Cigar          | pall-mall    | cain  | bolivar      |
| Job           | lawyer    | analyst | fisherman |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | horror  | drama     |
| Nationality   | turkish | spanish    | mexican      |

