.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, r&b, electronic
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, nurse
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, superhero
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, amber, ebony
1. the person watching documentary movies is the fisherman##1
2. the person who likes amber is on the right of the fan of house##1
3. the nurse is the fan of electronic##1
4. the fan of electronic is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes apricot is the fan of house##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the coach##1
7. the fisherman is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Music-Genre         | electronic | house     | r&b   |
| Job           | nurse       | fisherman   | coach     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | documentary | superhero |
| Color           | ebony      | apricot         | amber  |

