The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, house, indie
3 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, rat
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, magic-tricks, singing
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
2. the owner of the ferret is in the middle##1
3. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Game          | chess | snooker       | whist |
| Music-Genre   | indie     | gospel       | house   |
| Pet           | frog      | ferret       | rat     |
| Hobby         | baking   | magic-tricks | singing  |

