2. the dressmaker is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |
| Food          | plum       | cherry         | broccoli   |
| Job           | accountant | police-officer | dressmaker |
| Sport   | water-polo     | skiing        | golf        |
