.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-8::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, puzzles, woodworking
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, family, spy
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, september, november
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, oliveros, dannemann
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
6. the old-henry-smoker is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | woodworking | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | spy         | family       |
| Birthday           | october      | november      | september         |
| Cigar     | oliveros      | dannemann         | old-henry          |

