.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, writing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, gospel, house
3 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, guinea-pig
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, water, mirinda
1. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person drinking water##1
4. the fan of funk is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the fan of house is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby       | cooking            | chess      | writing  |
| Music-Genre         | house | funk | gospel |
| Pet         | goat               | guinea-pig | goldfish |
| Beverage   | water             | mirinda       | coffee      |

