.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, electrician, scientist
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, green, orange
There are 3 different nationalities: british, french, russian
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, fanta
1. the person who likes green is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the electrician is on the far right##1
5. the chef is on the left of the russian##1
6. the french is on the left of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Job           | scientist | chef         | electrician |
| Color   | ivory      | green | orange     |
| Nationality   | british   | french       | russian     |
| Beverage           | fanta    | almond-milk         | hot-chocolate        |

