.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, journalist, videographer
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, cycling, rugby
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, ivory, red
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, bus, helicopter
1. the person who likes red is on the right of the journalist##1
2. the videographer is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
5. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the videographer##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Job           | journalist | videographer | architect |
| Sport   | rugby        | cycling       | soccer     |
| Color   | ivory     | red         | apricot     |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus          | boat      |

