The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person playing billiard##1
2. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the fan of punk##1
4. the person playing chess is the italian##1
5. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
6. the brazilian is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Game         | bridge | billiard | chess   |
| Nationality           | brazilian     | japanese    | italian   |
| Music-Genre   | metal         | punk    | dubstep   |
| Sport         | cricket       | sailing | badminton |

