.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-14::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, lavender, apricot
There 3 different types of food: garlic, lime, strawberry
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, sudoku, traveling
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daffodil, orchid
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who likes lavender is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person eating lime##1
5. the person who likes apricot is the person who growsorchid##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| Color    | light-blue | lavender     | apricot      |
| Food        | garlic | lime       | strawberry |
| Hobby       | sudoku | collecting | traveling  |
| Flower   | daffodil    | balloon-flower   | orchid  |

