.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-17::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, mirinda
There 3 different types of food: mango, pear, peas
3 different games are played: scrabble, domino, mah-jongg
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, weightlifting, ice-hockey
1. the person playing domino is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person eating mango##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person eating peas is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Beverage      | mirinda      | milk    | cola    |
| Food          | peas         | pear    | mango   |
| Game           | scrabble | mah-jongg | domino |
| Sport   | ice-hockey         | climbing     | weightlifting    |

