There 3 different types of food: peach, pumpkin, strawberry
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, jazz, rock
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, filmmaking, baking
1. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person eating peach##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of rock is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |
| Pet      | hamster  | goldfish   | guinea-pig  |
| Food          | pumpkin   | strawberry | peach   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz      | disco      | rock    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | fishing    | baking |

