.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-19::.
City: marseilles, hamburg, liverpool
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, reading, board-games
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae, salsa
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, water-polo, weightlifting
1. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the fan of reggae is the person traveling to hamburg##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| City      | hamburg         | liverpool     | marseilles     |
| Hobby           | reading        | board-games | woodworking |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | salsa   | dubstep    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | rugby   | water-polo |

