.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, potato, tomato
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, roller, train
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, folk, r&b
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, iced-tea
1. the person eating tomato is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food          | tomato     | potato    | avocado    |
| Transport         | van | train | roller     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | folk      | r&b        |
| Beverage         | 7up   | almond-milk   | iced-tea |

 